	<h2>My Story</h2>
	<p>
		My journey as a traveler began in 2016 when I took my first solo trip across Northern India. 
		What started as a simple exploration quickly evolved into a lifelong passion. Since then, 
		I've been fortunate enough to explore various parts of Southeast Asia, trekking through the 
		Himalayas, riding motorcycles through the winding roads of Vietnam, and discovering hidden 
		beaches in Thailand.
	</p>
	<p>
		When I'm not traveling, you'll find me on my motorcycle exploring the diverse landscapes of India. 
		There's something incredibly freeing about feeling the wind against your face as you navigate through 
		mountain passes or coastal highways. My Royal Enfield has been my faithful companion on countless adventures, 
		from the high-altitude deserts of Ladakh to the lush Western Ghats.
	</p>

