	<h2>My Travel Philosophy</h2>
	<p>
		I believe that travel is more than just visiting tourist attractions. It's about immersing yourself in local cultures, 
		connecting with people from different backgrounds, and gaining new perspectives that broaden your understanding of the world.
	</p>
	<p>
		Whether it's sharing a meal with locals in a small village, participating in traditional festivals, or simply 
		sitting in a local tea shop observing daily life, these authentic connections are what make travel truly meaningful.
	</p>

